Class DelpArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.arg.delp.syntax.DelpArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.tweety.commons.Formula

    public class DelpArgument
extends Object
implements net.sf.tweety.commons.Formula
    This class models a DeLP argument which comprises of a set of defeasible rules (the support) and a literal (the conclusion).
    Author:
    Matthias Thimm
